            rdfs:label "District"@en .


###  https://www.michaeldebellis.com/dp/Domain
dp:Domain rdf:type owl:Class ;
          rdfs:comment "A business or problem domain that owns and governs one or more Data Products."@en ,
                       "Data Product usage: Domains provide the organizational context within which Data Products are defined, owned, and governed."@en ;
          rdfs:label "Domain"@en ;
          skos:definition "A domain is a coherent problem space within an organization that reflects a specific area of business capability, knowledge, and language. Domains provide the conceptual foundation for defining bounded contexts and data products, and align technical systems with business concerns."@en ,
                          "An organizational domain representing a coherent area of business responsibility and meaning."@en .


