                                 skos:definition "A cross-functional team responsible for optimizing advertising performance and revenue impact across StreamForge data products and analytics pipelines."@en ;
                                 skos:editorialNote "Created to improve RAG responses for ownership, responsibility, and monetization lineage questions."@en ;
                                 skos:note "This individual and its description are synthetic example data used for the StreamForge demonstration."@en .


