###  https://www.michaeldebellis.com/dp/Data_Steward_Role
dp:Data_Steward_Role rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                              <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Role> ;
                     dcterms:source "Strengholt, Piethein. Data Management at Scale: Modern Data Architecture with Data Mesh and Data Fabric. O’Reilly Media (Kindle Edition), pp. 369–371."@en ;
                     rdfs:label "Data steward"@en ;
                     skos:definition "Helps ensure that data policies and standards are followed; often serves as a subject matter expert for a specific type of data."@en ;
                     skos:editorialNote "Definition adapted from Strengholt (Data Management at Scale), pp. 369–371."@en .


###  https://www.michaeldebellis.com/dp/Data_User_Role
dp:Data_User_Role rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
