                               dcterms:description "Accuracy and coverage metrics for aggregated creator analytics."@en ;
                               rdfs:comment "Coverage: >= 99% of active creators have daily rows. Accuracy: revenue proxy within +/- 3% of monthly finance reconciliation (where applicable)."@en ;
                               rdfs:label "SF Creator Insights Quality"@en .


