                                                    dcterms:description "A scheduled analytics pipeline run that computes the executive 'Creator Growth' metric by aggregating creator KPIs from the SF Creator Insights Dataset. This activity produces the metric snapshot used in executive dashboards and strategic reporting."@en ,
